      <title>First Quantum 预计将在几周内运送被困的巴拿马铜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/first-quantum-expects-to-ship-trapped-panama-copper-within-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[First Quantum Minerals Ltd. 预计在未来几周内获得巴拿马官员的授权，出售其旗舰矿所在港口附近储存的超过 120,000 吨铜精矿。]]></description>
